Re: MP3 player(the physical kind) supporting Unicode or UTF-
by ダラゴスちゃん » Mon 09.26.2011 7:30 pm Anything with rockbox on it! Just install the font pack and use a UTF-16 supporting font. There are plenty!
ダラゴスちゃん
